<p>
<h1>Mobile Bash 9/1/03</h1>
<h2>From <a href="http://vulnax.users.btopenworld.com/bash-repts.htm#Sorcerer%20War%2022/8/02">Vulnax's Vault of Virtual 
Veracity</a></h2>
<p>
Not a good day for some ... Three major magic-users bit the dust but one was avenged as the killer himself was killed! The 
bash succeeded after the last mobile was summoned and slaughtered.
<p>
The bash started well with 6 players on and Puddy as the <font color="#fc54fc">bash-general</font>. As the 100 mobiles left 
mark was reached the game crashed! On resetting Hawumph allowed the bash to restart with some different players on, 7 in 
number, and no general as the vote was tied.
<p> 
<table bgcolor=black cellpadding=5><tr><td>
<pre>
<font color="#fcfcfc">qw</font><font color="#a8a8a8">
</font><font color="#fc5454">Hawumph the </font><font color="#5454fc">onomatopoeic</font><font color="#fc5454"> wizard</font><font color="#a8a8a8">
</font><font color="#a80000">Fallout the superhero</font><font color="#a8a8a8">
</font><font color="#a80000">Dblhelix the swordsman</font><font color="#a8a8a8">
</font><font color="#a80000">Teneighty the swordsman</font><font color="#a8a8a8">
</font><font color="#a80000">Pippin the swordsman</font><font color="#a8a8a8">
</font><font color="#a80000">Davidbrent the sorcerer</font><font color="#a8a8a8">
</font><font color="#a80000">Puddy the heroine</font><font color="#a8a8a8">
</font><font color="#a80000">Gilgamesh the dragonfly-slaying patriarch
</font></pre>
</td></tr></table>
<p>
A small team of three or four wiped out the rats in short order, giving a kill rate of:
<p>
<Table bgcolor="black" cellpadding=5>
<tr><TD><tt><font color="#5454fc">*</font><font color="#a85400">Hawumph the </font><font 
color="#5454fc">onomatopoeic</font><font color="#a85400"> wizard shouts "</font><font color="#fcfc54">Gilgamesh 31 kills, 
Davidbrent 19, 1080 21, Fallout & Puddy 6, Dblhelix 3</font><font color="#a85400">".</font></tt></td></tr>
</table>
<p>
Pippin had still yet to kill something!
<p>
The total soon fell down to 75 and then 50 mobiles left. 
<p>
<table bgcolor=black cellpadding=5><tr><td>
<pre>
<font color="#5454fc">*</font><font color="#fcfcfc">obit
</font><font color="#a8a8a8">The following players have died in fights this reset:
	Fallout the dragon-slaying sorcerer, killed by </font><font color="#a800a8">2 apes</font><font color="#a8a8a8">,
 Dblheliz the hero, killed by the </font><font color="#a800a8">giant snake</font><font color="#a8a8a8">.
</font></pre>
</td></tr></table>
 
<p>
With the evil twins and some of the keep left, along with sealife and the death of a magic-user, it looked a bit harder. <p>
Soon we saw:
<p>
<Table bgcolor="black" cellpadding=5>
<tr><TD><tt><font color="#5454fc">*For your information: there are 10 mobiles still alive.</font></tt></td></tr>
</table>
<p> 
... and then 9 in 35 mins, by which time Davibrent had been made de-facto <font color="#fc54fc">bash-general</font>! The 
curse of the <font color="#fc54fc">bash-general</font> falls again ...
<p>
<table bgcolor=black cellpadding=5><tr><td>
<pre>
