<font color="#a80000">You hit the crocodile (5-9).</font>
<font color="#A8A8A8">The crocodile looks seriously injured.</font>
<font color="#FC5454">The crocodile hits you (</font><font color="#a80000">11</font><font color="#FC5454">/</font><font 
