<font color="#fc5454"><span style="background:#a80000; color:#000000;">You feel your life leaving...</span></font>
<font color="#fc5454"><span style="background:#a80000; color:#000000;">The crocodile has killed you.</span></font>
</font></pre>
</td></tr></table>
<p>
Whoops! One dead bash general. The last mobile was holed up in a tomb and no one seemed to know how to open the tomb. 
Repeated summons were tried but failed. Then <font color="#a80000">someone</font> attacked Vulnax the warlock with a 
longsword, and when the other players tried to help some unfortunate person managed <b>kill all</b> instead of kill invis or 
similar. So, with multiple attacks Vulnax succumbed and shuffled off her mortal coil. As the last mobile was awaited, Corwin 
polished off Fallout, the invisible killer of Vulnax.
<p> 
<table bgcolor=black cellpadding=5><tr><td>
<pre>
