 Fallout the dragon-slaying sorcerer, killed by </font><font color="#a800a8">2 apes</font><font color="#a8a8a8">,
 Dblheliz the hero, killed by the </font><font color="#a800a8">giant snake</font><font color="#a8a8a8">.
