<p>
Then <b>the</b> message flashed up:
<p>
<Table bgcolor="black" cellpadding=5>
<tr><TD><tt><font color="#5454FC">*</font><font color="#FCFCFC">You feel as if a tremendous evil has been rid from The Land! No 
